{"parentUuid":"22c19e12-e0af-46f8-a30b-cf02321fe1c6","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a9897bafc5c9b12b7","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcvwaU6HY6xwu93Y2xxKj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01QXFQCW2Awz8X1ubQPH1m38","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/implementation-progress.md","content":"# Implementation progress — GET /v1/usage/daily\n\n## Environment note\n- `python`/`poetry run` are unavailable in this sandbox shell (no `python`\n  shim; `poetry env use` fails the same way). Working venv created at\n  `/tmp/claude-1000/.../scratchpad/venv` via `/home/brett/.local/bin/python3.12\n  -m venv` + `pip install` of the exact pins from `pyproject.toml`. Use\n  `<venv>/bin/python -m pytest ...` for all test runs this session.\n\n## Unit 1 — `src/api/schemas/usage_daily.py` (DONE)\n- Tests written first: `tests/test_schemas_usage_daily.py` (25 tests:\n  `parse_daily_date` valid/missing/malformed/out-of-range/boundary-inclusive,\n  `day_window_for` month-rollover + leap-year (pure helper, decoupled from\n  the sliding `[today-90d,today+1d]` range so it isn't flaky), query-param\n  `extra=forbid`, response-model `extra=forbid`).\n- Confirmed red: `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'src.api.schemas.usage_daily'`.\n- Implemented `src/api/schemas/usage_daily.py`: `DailyUsageQueryParams`\n  (`date: str | None`, `extra=\"forbid\"`), `parse_daily_date` (anchored\n  `^\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}$` regex -> `date.fromisoformat` calendar check ->\n  `[today_utc-90d, today_utc+1d]` range check, all raising\n  `HTTPException(400)`), `day_window_for` (pure UTC day-window helper),\n  `DailyMetricCount`/`DailyUsageResponse` response models (`extra=\"forbid\"`).\n- Green: T1: tests written+red -> code -> green (25/25 passed).\n\n## NEXT\n- Unit 2: `usage_repo.aggregate_daily_event_counts` + service + route +\n  `main.py` wiring, driven by\n  `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (write first, confirm red\n  against real Postgres via testcontainers, then implement).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":632,"cache_read_input_tokens":115691,"output_tokens":919,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":632},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":919,"cache_read_input_tokens":115691,"cache_creation_input_tokens":632,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":632,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcvwaSBC9bgqZrrJGPN1x","attributionAgent":"implementation","type":"assistant","uuid":"ddb713ba-c8a7-475c-9b1d-eab5197df8f6","timestamp":"2026-07-11T20:59:23.308Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
