{"parentUuid":"48403e30-f32c-4824-bb43-33e9f3f0b117","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"31d62281-78eb-4b7d-bb8c-b1ec8a71c6f0","agentId":"a9897bafc5c9b12b7","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XSrKo1Ke387az1np35bpQ2","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/implementation-progress.md has been updated successfully. (file state is current in your context — no need to Read it back)"}]},"uuid":"967facf0-f863-4d4d-aff8-c6a6805627ea","timestamp":"2026-07-11T21:01:57.811Z","toolUseResult":{"filePath":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/implementation-progress.md","oldString":"## NEXT\n- Unit 2: `usage_repo.aggregate_daily_event_counts` + service + route +\n  `main.py` wiring, driven by\n  `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (write first, confirm red\n  against real Postgres via testcontainers, then implement).","newString":"## Unit 2 — repo + service + route + main.py wiring (DONE)\n- Tests written first: `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (15\n  tests: AC1 multi-metric/multi-customer/multi-bucket aggregation, AC2\n  empty-day-200, AC3 missing-date-400, AC4 malformed-date-400, AC5\n  out-of-range-400, AC6 unknown-param-422, AC7 cross-tenant isolation, AC8\n  auth-required-401, AC9 ingest-key-not-admin-gated, AC10 UTC half-open day\n  boundary, AC11 no-regression to POST /v1/events + GET /v1/usage, AC12\n  usage.daily.read log shape, AC13 Tier-2 throttle wiring, AC14 OpenAPI\n  documents the route, AC15 forced-repo-error generic-500 fail-closed).\n- Confirmed red: 14/15 failed (404s — route not mounted; one ImportError for\n  the forced-error test's `usage_daily_service` import).\n- Implemented: `src/repositories/usage_repo.py` (additive\n  `DailyMetricCount` dataclass + `aggregate_daily_event_counts`, existing\n  functions untouched), `src/services/usage_daily_service.py`\n  (`get_daily_usage` — no error-swallowing try/except, matches\n  `usage_export_service.prepare_export` posture), `src/api/routes/usage_daily.py`\n  (`GET /v1/usage/daily`, `_require_authenticated_and_throttled` sibling —\n  auth then Tier-2, no admin gate), `src/main.py` (one new import + one\n  `app.include_router(usage_daily_router)` line, existing router lines\n  untouched).\n- Green: T2: tests written+red -> code -> green (15/15 integration passed).\n\n## NEXT\n- Run the full existing suite (unit + integration) for no-regression (AC11),\n  then coverage gate check, then the pre-report self-check (diff-vs-plan,\n  security quick scan) and `.pipeline/surface-delta.md`.","originalFile":"# Implementation progress — GET /v1/usage/daily\n\n## Environment note\n- `python`/`poetry run` are unavailable in this sandbox shell (no `python`\n  shim; `poetry env use` fails the same way). Working venv created at\n  `/tmp/claude-1000/.../scratchpad/venv` via `/home/brett/.local/bin/python3.12\n  -m venv` + `pip install` of the exact pins from `pyproject.toml`. Use\n  `<venv>/bin/python -m pytest ...` for all test runs this session.\n\n## Unit 1 — `src/api/schemas/usage_daily.py` (DONE)\n- Tests written first: `tests/test_schemas_usage_daily.py` (25 tests:\n  `parse_daily_date` valid/missing/malformed/out-of-range/boundary-inclusive,\n  `day_window_for` month-rollover + leap-year (pure helper, decoupled from\n  the sliding `[today-90d,today+1d]` range so it isn't flaky), query-param\n  `extra=forbid`, response-model `extra=forbid`).\n- Confirmed red: `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'src.api.schemas.usage_daily'`.\n- Implemented `src/api/schemas/usage_daily.py`: `DailyUsageQueryParams`\n  (`date: str | None`, `extra=\"forbid\"`), `parse_daily_date` (anchored\n  `^\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}$` regex -> `date.fromisoformat` calendar check ->\n  `[today_utc-90d, today_utc+1d]` range check, all raising\n  `HTTPException(400)`), `day_window_for` (pure UTC day-window helper),\n  `DailyMetricCount`/`DailyUsageResponse` response models (`extra=\"forbid\"`).\n- Green: T1: tests written+red -> code -> green (25/25 passed).\n\n## NEXT\n- Unit 2: `usage_repo.aggregate_daily_event_counts` + service + route +\n  `main.py` wiring, driven by\n  `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (write first, confirm red\n  against real Postgres via testcontainers, then implement).\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":22,"oldLines":8,"newStart":22,"newLines":29,"lines":["   `DailyMetricCount`/`DailyUsageResponse` response models (`extra=\"forbid\"`)."," - Green: T1: tests written+red -> code -> green (25/25 passed)."," ","+## Unit 2 — repo + service + route + main.py wiring (DONE)","+- Tests written first: `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (15","+  tests: AC1 multi-metric/multi-customer/multi-bucket aggregation, AC2","+  empty-day-200, AC3 missing-date-400, AC4 malformed-date-400, AC5","+  out-of-range-400, AC6 unknown-param-422, AC7 cross-tenant isolation, AC8","+  auth-required-401, AC9 ingest-key-not-admin-gated, AC10 UTC half-open day","+  boundary, AC11 no-regression to POST /v1/events + GET /v1/usage, AC12","+  usage.daily.read log shape, AC13 Tier-2 throttle wiring, AC14 OpenAPI","+  documents the route, AC15 forced-repo-error generic-500 fail-closed).","+- Confirmed red: 14/15 failed (404s — route not mounted; one ImportError for","+  the forced-error test's `usage_daily_service` import).","+- Implemented: `src/repositories/usage_repo.py` (additive","+  `DailyMetricCount` dataclass + `aggregate_daily_event_counts`, existing","+  functions untouched), `src/services/usage_daily_service.py`","+  (`get_daily_usage` — no error-swallowing try/except, matches","+  `usage_export_service.prepare_export` posture), `src/api/routes/usage_daily.py`","+  (`GET /v1/usage/daily`, `_require_authenticated_and_throttled` sibling —","+  auth then Tier-2, no admin gate), `src/main.py` (one new import + one","+  `app.include_router(usage_daily_router)` line, existing router lines","+  untouched).","+- Green: T2: tests written+red -> code -> green (15/15 integration passed).","+"," ## NEXT","-- Unit 2: `usage_repo.aggregate_daily_event_counts` + service + route +","-  `main.py` wiring, driven by","-  `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (write first, confirm red","-  against real Postgres via testcontainers, then implement).","+- Run the full existing suite (unit + integration) for no-regression (AC11),","+  then coverage gate check, then the pre-report self-check (diff-vs-plan,","+  security quick scan) and `.pipeline/surface-delta.md`."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"48403e30-f32c-4824-bb43-33e9f3f0b117","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
