{"parentUuid":"14a101c4-b9b1-4cf3-bb7f-d5ade4eab855","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"6520cc4a-a27d-4422-a981-cada3a1f0a88","agentId":"a9897bafc5c9b12b7","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01C1ThczHyGYtaaeKk3Rb6yQ","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Implementation progress — GET /v1/usage/daily\n2\t\n3\t## Environment note\n4\t- `python`/`poetry run` are unavailable in this sandbox shell (no `python`\n5\t  shim; `poetry env use` fails the same way). Working venv created at\n6\t  `/tmp/claude-1000/.../scratchpad/venv` via `/home/brett/.local/bin/python3.12\n7\t  -m venv` + `pip install` of the exact pins from `pyproject.toml`. Use\n8\t  `<venv>/bin/python -m pytest ...` for all test runs this session.\n9\t\n10\t## Unit 1 — `src/api/schemas/usage_daily.py` (DONE)\n11\t- Tests written first: `tests/test_schemas_usage_daily.py` (25 tests:\n12\t  `parse_daily_date` valid/missing/malformed/out-of-range/boundary-inclusive,\n13\t  `day_window_for` month-rollover + leap-year (pure helper, decoupled from\n14\t  the sliding `[today-90d,today+1d]` range so it isn't flaky), query-param\n15\t  `extra=forbid`, response-model `extra=forbid`).\n16\t- Confirmed red: `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'src.api.schemas.usage_daily'`.\n17\t- Implemented `src/api/schemas/usage_daily.py`: `DailyUsageQueryParams`\n18\t  (`date: str | None`, `extra=\"forbid\"`), `parse_daily_date` (anchored\n19\t  `^\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}$` regex -> `date.fromisoformat` calendar check ->\n20\t  `[today_utc-90d, today_utc+1d]` range check, all raising\n21\t  `HTTPException(400)`), `day_window_for` (pure UTC day-window helper),\n22\t  `DailyMetricCount`/`DailyUsageResponse` response models (`extra=\"forbid\"`).\n23\t- Green: T1: tests written+red -> code -> green (25/25 passed).\n24\t\n25\t## Unit 2 — repo + service + route + main.py wiring (DONE)\n26\t- Tests written first: `tests/integration/test_usage_daily_endpoint.py` (15\n27\t  tests: AC1 multi-metric/multi-customer