`git ls-files --others\n    --exclude-standard` show exactly the plan's 7 files (schemas/service/route\n    new, `usage_repo.py`/`main.py` additive-mod, 2 new test files) plus\n    pre-existing unrelated modifications to `.claude/settings.json`/`PROJECT.md`\n    (`PROJECT.md`'s diff is the feature-brief swap itself, already present\n    before this session started).\n  - **Hardcoded secrets**: grep across all 7 changed/new files — no hits.\n  - **Missing RLS**: `aggregate_daily_event_counts` scopes `WHERE api_key_id =\n    :api_key_id` first (bound from `principal.api_key_id`, never client\n    input), inside `scoped_transaction` (RLS backstop) — confirmed by reading\n    the function and the cross-tenant integration test passing.\n  - **Unsanitized inputs**: the only input (`date`) flows\n    `DailyUsageQueryParams` (`extra=\"forbid\"`) -> `parse_daily_date` (anchored\n    regex + calendar + range check) before any use; no raw\n    `request.query_params` access in the route/service.\n- App boot verified twice this session: `python -c \"import src.main\"`\n  succeeds, and a real `uvicorn src.main:app` process answers `GET /health`\n  with 200 `{\"status\":\"ok\"}`.\n- `.pipeline/surface-delta.md` rewritten for this feature (the file on disk\n  was stale content from the prior quota-admin feature run — overwritten,\n  not appended).\n\n## STATUS: DONE\n\nAll 3 units complete, full suite green (253 passed / 0 failed / 89% branch\ncoverage), app boots, surface-delta + progress notes current. Ready for the\nsecurity/testing/documentation stages."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1634,"cache_read_input_tokens":162678,"output_tokens":1371,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1634},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":