nts/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/src/main.py` — one new import + one `include_router` line; nothing else changed.\n\n**Verification:** Full suite (`pytest -q -m \"not perf\" --cov=src --cov-branch`) run twice this session: **253 passed, 3 skipped, 1 deselected, 0 failed**, coverage **89%** (new modules at 100%). App boots cleanly (`import src.main` and a live `uvicorn` process both confirmed; `/health` → 200). All 15 acceptance criteria (AC1–AC15) are addressed and test-covered. Pre-report self-check passed: no hardcoded secrets, `api_key_id`-first RLS scoping confirmed, `date` input flows through schema + imperative validation before any use, diff matches the plan's file list exactly.\n\n`.pipeline/surface-delta.md` and `.pipeline/implementation-progress.md` are current (surface-delta.md was stale from a prior feature run and has been overwritten for this feature).\n\nNo migration was needed (plan confirms none), no new dependency was added."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":363,"cache_read_input_tokens":165792,"output_tokens":1179,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":363},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":1179,"cache_read_input_tokens":165792,"cache_creation_input_tokens":363,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":363,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcvxjH5s95169dRADd5Po","attributionAgent":"implementation","type":"assistant","uuid":"05e5ce0a-d31c-4370-a75f-c43fe03fad44","timestamp":"2026-07-11T21:14:31.382Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usa